title: Death to the McKenzies - Called Drum Technique
description:
Crestline, CA based Alternative Rock band Death to the McKenzies, has been drescribed as "a little punk rock, a little grunge 
(inspired by the master himself, Kurt Cobain), a little doowop, a little new wave, a little marijuana, a little "Karate Kid," 
and powerful biting rock."

The band has 5 studio albums to date, with a 6th (Called, Drum Technique)being released exclusively through the bands "Band Camp" page 11/10/2015 and 
then at all online retailers (including Spotify) 12/01/2015.
